@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yjwbue(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.50 * (tmp / wp.abs(v1 + 0.29)))
    v2 = wp.cos((0.13 * (v1 + 0.69 * v2 + 0.99)))
    tmp = ((0.91 / 0.99) - wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.38)))
    v2 = 0.31
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.47 / v2 + 0.89)) - v0)
    data[tid] = v0
